TIP: That tiny sliver of white at the top left is because you're probably initializing your sprite display list to all $00. To make it disappear, initialize all Y coordinates to something between $F0 and $FF.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Mon May 03, 2010 6:09 pm</p><hr />
