Your code for Hello World needs to do all this:<br /><br />Wait for the machine to 'warm up' by waiting for the vblank flag to be set twice.<br />Turn off the screen.<br />Clear all the name tables.<br />Decide where to put the text on the screen.<br />Copy the text to the screen.<br />Wait for Vblank.<br />Turn on the screen.<br /><br />more to come...<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Mon May 03, 2010 12:00 pm</p><hr />
